Thanks to everyone that helped :).
This map is my third bhop map that I have released. It is a moderately short egypt theme easy/fun bhop map with 2 ljs. Its built with legit in mind so should be suitable for any type of bhop you like.

Please rate and give feedback so I can improve my future maps :).


NOTE: THIS MAP IS THE FIXED OR FINAL VERSION OF EGYPTTEMPLE IT IS NOT LIKELY TO BE CHANGED UNLESS A SEVERE BUG IS PRESENT.
